text:
Khao Soi Gai is pretty hard to find in SG; it's my favourite nothern thai dish. This is where I come for my fix.

It's good. Rich flavour, succulent chicken. Quite delicious, and I'm glad this stall is a bus ride away from me. Note the opening hours. It's mainly a lunch spot.
Authentic Thai Style Curry Noodle. The Lor Mee was also good too :)
